{"tid":1732784,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"關於Poly入面既CCTV","createTime":"2019-11-18T03:11:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T10:50:28.000Z","uid":79654,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ddc954dc1b99293faed111e9be52940ec0506e71","tid":1732784,"uid":79654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:11:45.000Z","msg":"我見好多人係度討論緊係咪應該換翻平民裝<br />\n但係係咪都要考慮埋入面既CCTV?<br />\n班狗做舉證果陣肯定會問Poly拎CCTV<br />\n你地睇個撚屌校長 消失左一日 一出黎就拍片叫人自首<br />\n所以Poly實全力配合俾撚曬啲CCTV班狗<br />\n<br />\n所以係咪應該都諗下點處理啲CCTV<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wgQK2rf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwgQK2rf.png&h=2261e1e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天佑手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"41720f29c6804ead80a460531d5b340c0b0663ed","tid":1732784,"uid":79654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:21:22.000Z","msg":"推(1/10)"},{"pid":"cbb0fd24df047f1017eebf0159e61a7c048b90a1","tid":1732784,"uid":79654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:21:35.000Z","msg":"推(2/10)"},{"pid":"49f592d183f90a32f05ea13b2f71966889531b0d","tid":1732784,"uid":79654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:21:46.000Z","msg":"推(3/10)"},{"pid":"f5ae7258528dd4fe95331ad6659f0031fe4adb0d","tid":1732784,"uid":79654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:21:59.000Z","msg":"推(4/10)"},{"pid":"99d79505c21f007e5e09c0133c97bed6894fd395","tid":1732784,"uid":79654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:22:11.000Z","msg":"推(5/10)"},{"pid":"520ad7078bb8d337541ef4880aeaf9fb103e3ecf","tid":1732784,"uid":79654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T03:22:21.000Z","msg":"推(6/10)"},{"pid":"cfa64b057c322129f5fe635b34ed00368b89